 tray, then place 6 dough discs onto tray. Place Varoma into position, insert Varoma tray, secure Varoma lid and steam <b>6 min\/Varoma\/speed 2<b>. Transfer pancakes into a separate thermal serving bowl or large plate and cover to keep warm. Repeat steaming with remaining dough discs, topping up water levels as needed.","To serve, place a small amount of hoi sin sauce and Sriracha (optional) onto steamed pancakes, top with 2 teaspoons shredded pork and garnish with pickled cucumber, coriander leaves and a slice of chilli."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"Marinade","content":["3 garlic cloves","3 cm fresh ginger, peeled","1 tsp Chinese five spice","3 spring onions\/shallots, trimmed and cut into pieces","30 g rice wine vinegar","30 g soy sauce","20 g honey","30 g hoi sin sauce, plus extra to serve","20 g sesame oil","30 g kecap manis","400 g pork loin steaks, cut into cubes (approx. 3 cm)"]},{"title":"Steamed pancakes","content":["170 g water","50 g white sugar","2 tsp dried instant yeast","300 g baker's flour, plus extra for dusting","1 tsp sea salt","¼ tsp baking powder","¼ tsp bicarbonate of soda","30 g sesame oil"]},{"title":"Quick pickled cucumber","content":["100 g rice wine vinegar","25 g sugar","¼ tsp sea salt","2 Lebanese cucumbers, cut into halves and peeled into ribbons"]},{"title":"Steaming and assembly","content":["1000 g water","20 g Sriracha sauce (optional) (see Tips)","fresh coriander, leaves only, to serve","2 fresh long red chillies, deseeded and cut into thin slices, to serve"]}],"id":"r103889","imageLink":"https:\/\/3.bp.blogspot.com\/-d3NXwst_9g0\/XZMv21cHLwI\/AAAAAAAAaXA\/eQ0BxL9p438-RpwPrqoLFcETVhbuIVuOwCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_r9acUocj0CRbzCWi.png","title":"Steamed pork pancakes (Bianca Mazur)","publishedAt":"2016-12-28T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"5.349 g","fat":"2.529 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"12.962 g","calories":"408 kJ \/ 97 kcal"},"usefulItems":"large ceramic or glass bowl, plastic wrap, bowl, kitchen towel, silicone brea